index.hero-description: We transform the best of innovations into new deposits of value: we are the architects of responsible technology.
index.whoarewe-desc: Since 2007, we help companies meet the challenges of new computer technologies. Because this field must combine passion and economic reality, our team relays the image of new organizations mixing technical experts, data scientists, organizational coaches, service designers and business specialists. Our culture provides our clients with keys to success in this period of economic and societal transition.
